These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, siglo, baccarat, prince
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the prince-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
5. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Cigar   | alhambra | siglo | prince | baccarat |
| Pet        | dog | goat   | mouse | horse    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, lily, marigold, balloon-flower
There are 4 different nationalities: french, german, nigerian, russian
1. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the french is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
4. the french is the person who growszinnia##1
5. the german is on the right of the nigerian##1
6. the french is the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Flower   | marigold | zinnia  | lily  | balloon-flower |
| Nationality   | russian    | french | nigerian | german    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, pomegranate, watermelon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, disco, funk, house
1. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
2. the person eating pomegranate is in an even position##4
3. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
4. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of funk##1
5. the fan of metal is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pomegranate | grapes    | carrot      |
| Music-Genre   | funk        | house     | metal | disco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, rose, begonia, marigold
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, folk, indie, reggae
1. the person who growsrose is between the fan of blues and the fan of reggae##2
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
3. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Flower         | marigold | tulip | rose | begonia |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | blues   | folk    | reggae  |

