.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, skateboard, subway, boat
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, indian, russian
1. the person driving the subway is on the right of the russian##1
2. the australian is the person driving the boat##1
3. the indian is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
6. the american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Transport   | skateboard  | jet-ski    | subway   | boat       |
| Nationality   | american | russian | indian | australian |

