.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, epic, time-travel
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, d&b, techno, dubstep
1. the fan of d&b is in an even position##4
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
3. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | documentary | time-travel | animation |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | d&b     | r&b  | techno  |

