.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, family, mystery, western
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, light-blue, apricot, ebony
1. the person who likes ebony is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person who likes ebony is the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
6. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | western | mystery | family    |
| Color     | ebony | apricot  | lilac     | light-blue |

