.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, mango, pepper, watermelon
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, dunhill, aristoff, bluemaster
1. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
2. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating mango##1
3. the game-smoker is between the dunhill-smoker and the person eating pepper##2
4. the game-smoker is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating pepper is the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | watermelon | mango   | cabbage | pepper |
| Cigar    | bluemaster     | dunhill | game     | aristoff  |

