.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, tea, water
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, argentine, brazilian, polish
1. the pakistani is in an even position##4
2. the brazilian is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the brazilian is on the left of the polish##1
4. the polish is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta   | water   | juice      | tea      |
| Nationality      | argentine | brazilian | polish | pakistani |

