.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-13::.
House: cape-cod, ranch-style, art-deco, victorian
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, motorbike, train
1. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the art-deco house##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
4. the ranch-style house is in an odd position##4
5. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| House   | ranch-style | cape-cod | art-deco | victorian  |
| Transport     | boat   | bike  | train  | motorbike |

