.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
City: hannover, rome, miami, hamburg
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goat, snake
1. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to hannover is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
6. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| City   | miami | hamburg | hannover | rome |
| Pet           | snake     | dog     | goat   | frog         |

