.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, tulip, zinnia, dahlia
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who growsdaisy is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who growstulip##2
2. the person who growszinnia is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Flower   | dahlia | tulip         | daisy   | zinnia |
| Sport   | soccer    | skateboarding | weightlifting | ice-hockey   |

