.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, chess, gardening, sudoku
4 different games are played: go, backgammon, chess, mah-jongg
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an even position##4
3. the person playing backgammon is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
5. the person playing backgammon is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person playing chess##2
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | sudoku   | gardening | board-games | chess    |
| Game   | chess | backgammon  | mah-jongg     | go |

