.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, indonesian, pakistani
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, soccer, cycling, snowboarding
1. the american is on the left of the pakistani##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the indonesian##1
5. the american is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | canadian | indonesian | american  | pakistani |
| Sport     | swimming      | cycling       | soccer | snowboarding     |

